    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Genre of works made of twigs, rushes, thin strips of wood, or other flexible material woven together; includes baskets, other vessels, and other items.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
